  The Defendant was sentenced to the following:

IMPOSED SENTENCE of: 

4 YEARS 6 MONTHS IMPRISONMENT (CREDIT - 1 days) to begin forthwith;
  -  1 YEAR 6 MONTHS OF INITIAL CONFINEMENT
  -  3 YEARS OF EXTENDED SUPERVISION;

CONDITIONS OF EXTENDED SUPERVISION:  
*Follow through with any treatment and/or counseling recommended by Agent;
*Maintain full time employment and/or combination of schooling .
*DNA sample to be provided if not yet previously done.
*Any other conditoin deemed appropriate by agent.
*Perform 100 hours community service.
*Not to operate a motor vehicle unless properly licensed.
*Attend Victim Impact Panel - completed on 8/19/15.
*D/L Revocation: 36 months;
*Ignition Interlock: 36 months;

BLOOD DRAW FEE: $35.00 (to be paid as a condition of probation - to be forwarded to City of Waukesha Police Department);

FINE  $1519.00 (apply cash bail and balance to be paid as a condition of extended supervision);

